UID:10003865-1783195200-1783202400@buffalobayou.org
SUMMARY:Bubbles and Fireworks Boat Tour
DESCRIPTION:Hop aboard BBP’s pontoon boat for perfect views of Houston’s spectacular fireworks show! \nAvoid the crowds and view the city’s fireworks extravaganza while floating along Buffalo Bayou and enjoying bubbly\, beer\, wine and light bites. We can only accommodate 21 lucky guests\, so register now! \nBoat tours leave from Allen’s Landing (1005 Commerce Street). \nCost: $150 per person \nNote: Children under the age of 4 are not allowed on the pontoon boat. \nPURCHASE TICKETS
URL:https://buffalobayou.org/event/2026-bubbles-and-fireworks-boat-tour/
LOCATION:ALLEN’S LANDING\, 1001 Commerce Street\, Houston\, TX\, 77002\, United States
CATEGORIES:Boat Tour,Seasonal Cruises
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://buffalobayou.org/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bluebayou_7492.jpg
END:VEVENT
